★ HIGH QUALITY - Cat feature toy made from safe,non-toxic. Eco-friendly material.All dyes are non-toxic and safe for your cats and our feather are all nature with less dyes.

★ PERFECT GIFT - Our cat wands make the ideal gift for anyone, including your own cat. What a great way to keep your cat healthy and suitable for life.Interactive toys engage the cat with you, and build trust and companionship between you and your pet.

★BUY WITH CONFIDENCE - Our philosophy and goal is to make all of the customers who purchase our products will come back a second time. Tell us directly any time when there is any problem with your cat teaser toys!
description: Cats could be your family members from the moment you keep them. So you need to spend time to play with them. This retractable cat teaser wand set is a good helper for you. The refills are easy to take on or off the rod. It is a wonderful gift for people who own a cat. Just enjoy hours playing with your cat in a super fun way.

- Brand: UEETEK.- Color: Multicolor.- Material: Plastic, wood and feather.- Length: 75 cm / 29.5 inch(Maximum); 45 cm / 17.7 inch(Minimum).- This teaser wand set includes 4 feather refills and 1 rod.- The handle is of ergonomic design, very comfortable to grip.- Telescopic rod design, convenient to stretch and shrink.- The rod is made of carbon fiber which features flexible, high strength and toughness.
